{"tid":2425654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"悼念吳孟達嗰班人，你地肯承認自己同「佢地」根本唔係同路人未？","createTime":"2021-02-27T13:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T14:18:05.000Z","uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b4c6de9386aff2c0340c9d170d3c6d3edaa9ecc7","tid":2425654,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:08:25.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾你地心入面都接受唔到「佢地」思想嗰種極端<br />\n我知你地係被迫做「佢地」既同路人，驚比人話你無人性，驚比人話你藍，驚比人話你無資格做香港人<br />\n但若果你心入面覺得悼念吳孟達係無問題既<br />\n到咗呢一刻你係時候承認你接受不了「佢地」呢種極端思想及行為<br />\n你地同「佢地」根本從來不是同路人"},{"pid":"bad0c289d2328f7438bb1971d80e39e211823dd5","tid":2425654,"uid":218793,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:09:33.000Z","msg":"是但啦，樓主全家比狗屌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LjjCJZj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLjjCJZj.png&h=d5c37d17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad367be11c661518b52bc24a83508230694e80fe","tid":2425654,"uid":148355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fVy0GMf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfVy0GMf.png&h=21e53139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n辛苦你了"},{"pid":"8ed36ac8af64a6cd3b791432f8e1613486681aea","tid":2425654,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vywqwqY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvywqwqY.gif&h=c5faffdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美中和好，反中撚炒哂車#3 -- 回憶小子<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1891475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1891475</a>"},{"pid":"b8ad54ddb987bb1c270701636c264b2e6266f5fd","tid":2425654,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:53:43.000Z","msg":"香港係屬於你地既香港，只不過呢兩年比「佢地」騎劫哂<br />\n你地有權悼念你地想悼念既人"},{"pid":"70fe9f5f119c6fe23d940fd8fc8724cb4c048fee","tid":2425654,"u